text.div:
NameFlagsCard.TypeDescription & Constraints
Extension 0..*ExtensionCommunication Opt-Out
communication-product 0..1CodeableConceptApplies opt-out for a specific product
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/communication-product
Binding: Engagement Product Value Set (extensible)
communication-mode 0..1CodeableConceptApplies opt-out for specific mode of communication (phone | sms | email | mail | chat)
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/communication-mode
Binding: Engagement Communication Mode Value Set (preferred)
conversation-type 0..1CodeableConceptApplies opt-out for a specific conversation type
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/conversation-type
Binding: Engagement Conversation Type Value Set (extensible)
communication-care-gap 0..1stringApplies opt-out for a specific care gap
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/communication-care-gap
stated-reason 0..1CodeableConceptRecorded reason the recipient requested the opt-out
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/stated-reason
valueCodeableConcept 0..1CodeableConceptValue of extension
Binding: Engagement Opt-Out Reason Value Set (extensible)
effective-period 0..1PeriodEffective period for the opt-out
URL: http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/effective-period
url 1..1uri"http://ibm.com/fhir/cdm/StructureDefinition/communication-opt-out"
value[x] 0..0
